Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=========Pre=========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.30,0:00:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往昔 大地豐裕 人們安居樂業
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.25,0:00:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但貪得無厭者將家禽果實據為己有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.07,0:00:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們在飢餓中哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.55,0:00:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一位勇者聞訊趕來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.80,0:00:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手持青炎長槍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.75,0:00:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刺穿貪得無厭者的心臟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.90,0:00:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自那之後 大地重獲生機
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.57,0:00:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貪得無厭者名為 達魯庫斯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.92,0:00:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者則名為 瓦爾基裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.92,0:00:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs32}Valkyria:女武神
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=========OP=========
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.71,0:01:14.61,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}輝く星たち　永遠を照らしてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.19,0:01:26.14,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}不確かな世界 その全て許すように
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.56,0:01:32.76,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}いくつ願いを紡いだら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.96,0:01:37.85,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}叶う日が来る？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.07,0:01:44.50,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}届け遙か空へ　明日へのキズナ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.72,0:01:51.35,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}手のひらに芽ばえた揺るがぬ光は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.78,0:01:59.50,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}私の希望の証と信じている
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.50,0:02:02.97,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}I'll pray forever
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.99,0:02:09.87,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1}抱きしめてる　Found my destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.71,0:01:14.61,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}閃耀的星辰  照亮了永恆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.19,0:01:26.14,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}像是寬恕了這整個不確定的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.56,0:01:32.76,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}只要不斷許下願望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.96,0:01:37.85,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}總有實現的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.07,0:01:44.50,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}去吧  向著遙遠的天空  通往明日的羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.72,0:01:51.35,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}手掌中萌發出堅定的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.78,0:01:59.50,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}我相信那是希望的證明
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.50,0:02:02.97,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}I'll pray forever
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.99,0:02:09.87,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1}緊緊抱於懷中　Found my destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=======PART A=======
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.02,0:02:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請保持鎮定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.27,0:02:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往不遠的蘭蒂格瑞絲城
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.12,0:02:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加利亞軍將保護大家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家保重
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.88,0:02:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就能重返家園
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.48,0:02:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭蒂格瑞絲城設有Ragnite和Ragn機油的配給站
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.54,0:02:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請保存好供應券
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.04,0:02:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漢斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.88,0:02:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗西婭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.08,0:02:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 艾麗西婭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.43,0:03:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡走丟可不是鬧著玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.66,0:03:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 漢斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.15,0:03:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凶殘的帝國軍會把你抓去吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.61,0:03:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用怕 艾麗西婭和自衛團的人會對付他們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.32,0:03:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.30,0:03:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了 布魯魯自衛團才不怕帝國軍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.68,0:03:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.92,0:03:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 帝國的將軍不好惹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.47,0:03:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前日聽說吉蘭達約要塞不到三天就被攻陷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.03,0:03:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是馬克西米利安准皇太子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.05,0:03:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無非是個花瓶總司令
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.37,0:03:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定弱不禁風
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.19,0:03:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但願如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.37,0:03:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是今天早上臨走前烤的麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.23,0:03:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.24,0:03:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉沒能幫上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.16,0:03:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼呢 自衛團的工作遠比麵包房重要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.75,0:04:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈夫去世後 店裡多虧有艾麗西婭照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.94,0:04:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗西婭烤的麵包 足以稱得上大師級了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.29,0:04:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路平安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.66,0:04:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗西婭也是 有事就聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.19,0:04:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗西婭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.35,0:04:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 蘇茜？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.14,0:04:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是有工作嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.22,0:04:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,間…間諜！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.26,0:04:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔伯斯橋旁 有個人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.51,0:04:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年紀很輕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.01,0:04:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.97,0:05:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詹姆和米格羅留在那裡看住他了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.95,0:05:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該還沒被發覺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.15,0:05:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊肯團長說他幾點回來？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.68,0:05:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午後？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.22,0:05:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼辦好 萬一間諜有武器的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.29,0:05:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可怕了 早知不參加什麼自衛團了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.76,0:05:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘇茜 這裡拜託
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.67,0:05:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗西婭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.31,0:05:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,間諜在哪兒？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.83,0:05:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是艾麗西婭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.62,0:05:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橋那邊 還是一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.38,0:05:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似在筆記本上寫些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.26,0:05:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筆記本？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.96,0:05:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對是間諜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.18,0:06:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.79,0:06:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢舉起手 把頭轉過來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.06,0:06:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是布魯魯自衛團
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.39,0:06:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡鬼鬼祟祟幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.19,0:06:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 閃光鱒的寫生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.71,0:06:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃光鱒？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.22,0:06:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道現在的情勢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.69,0:06:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼不妥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.69,0:06:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筆記本給我看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.20,0:06:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼的暗號…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.98,0:06:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非你不認識閃光鱒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.53,0:06:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們每年春季洄游
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.20,0:06:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面畫的是閃光鱒的花紋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.36,0:06:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布魯魯近郊的閃光鱒 魚身花紋非常特別
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.84,0:06:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且今天春光明媚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.76,0:06:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.73,0:06:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筆記本沒收
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.31,0:06:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.09,0:06:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.66,0:06:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有話到自衛團的拘役所裡說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.43,0:07:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到 寫生都被禁止嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.84,0:07:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝國軍都像你這樣呆頭呆腦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.72,0:07:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝國軍？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.41,0:07:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.24,0:07:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.63,0:07:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了 這樣也想當間諜？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.75,0:07:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 還沒問尊姓大名呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.54,0:07:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.00,0:07:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維爾金
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.35,0:07:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維爾金…鞏特爾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.76,0:07:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰想出這個名字的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.23,0:07:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道的話我來告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.17,0:07:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在布魯魯 自稱鞏特爾需要有一定資格
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.83,0:07:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者的資格
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.36,0:07:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還不夠格 間諜先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.48,0:07:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,間諜？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.35,0:07:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說我？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.09,0:07:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厚顏無恥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.96,0:07:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不懂怎麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.48,0:07:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我何時變成間諜了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.33,0:07:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉…間諜？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.87,0:07:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現如今還想矇混過關…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.13,0:07:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊急集合？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.65,0:08:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.58,0:08:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先走一步 帶他回城
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.32,0:08:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別讓他溜了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.88,0:08:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包在我們身上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.38,0:08:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼情況？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.49,0:08:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.30,0:08:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.33,0:08:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道也不可能告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.03,0:08:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成 你們也認為我是間諜？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.77,0:08:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心 米格羅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.10,0:08:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙想和我們套近乎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.47,0:08:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.92,0:08:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本沒這打算啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.51,0:08:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們看起來剛剛15歲出頭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.68,0:08:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經加入自衛團了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.80,0:08:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 別小瞧人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.60,0:08:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加利亞人從小學就接受軍事訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.72,0:08:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連坦克都能開
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.13,0:08:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詹姆 那輛老坦克不是壞了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.78,0:08:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用對敵人實話實說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.53,0:09:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是坐了下炮手席吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.53,0:09:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事後讓人知道了好丟人的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.38,0:09:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴！米格羅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.83,0:09:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小少爺 這不是小少爺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.81,0:09:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莎小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.75,0:09:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體還好嗎 應該快了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.56,0:09:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托您的福 一切順利
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.50,0:09:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見過伊莎拉小姐了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.18,0:09:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒 正打算去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.32,0:09:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.05,0:09:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說少爺回來前絕不離開老屋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.03,0:09:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊莎拉還是那麼倔強
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.56,0:09:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家是惦記你這個哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.93,0:09:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小少爺 你這手是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.59,0:09:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…事出有因
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.65,0:09:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小少爺又搞什麼惡作劇了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.02,0:09:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 說你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.85,0:09:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以啊 別擅自亂跑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.98,0:09:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 瑪莎小姐要注意身子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.72,0:09:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小少爺！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.22,0:10:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有跡象表明 帝國軍在貝羅裡克森林集結
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.84,0:10:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方一鼓作氣的話 不出半日就能攻到這裡啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.92,0:10:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.14,0:10:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊肯團長 正規軍還是按兵不動？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.27,0:10:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還須24小時才能下達出動命令
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.22,0:10:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了 為什麼如此費時？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.19,0:10:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從整體戰局考慮 可能認為這裡戰略價值較低吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.09,0:10:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們把城池拱手相讓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.86,0:10:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先發制人的話 必能重創帝國軍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.63,0:10:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邁克爾 當務之急是疏散民眾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.07,0:10:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於下午的部署…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.35,0:10:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.36,0:10:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…艾麗西婭？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.18,0:11:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詹姆 大夥兒有重要事商量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.93,0:11:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過會再說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.72,0:11:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.19,0:11:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實…我們剛才在塔伯斯橋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.20,0:11:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗西婭 現在沒空討論孩子的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.51,0:11:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去去就回
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.67,0:11:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙 跑過去和一個女人說話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.01,0:11:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.64,0:11:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我認識的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.33,0:11:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼下事務繁雜 暫時在這裡等吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.49,0:11:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能提個問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.04,0:11:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.80,0:11:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布魯魯這裡也要開戰？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.52,0:11:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說 是你裡應外合！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.64,0:11:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.26,0:11:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎麼知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.61,0:11:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警報響起後你匆忙趕回去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.68,0:11:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自衛團的人紛紛集結
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.86,0:11:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此想來 只能是壞消息
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.73,0:12:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你來說卻不盡然吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.13,0:12:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能放了我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.41,0:12:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在等我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.64,0:12:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就回來 讓我去好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.59,0:12:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開…開什麼玩笑 誰會相信這種鬼話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.98,0:12:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詹姆 米格羅 看住他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.26,0:12:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多留個心眼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.07,0:12:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.78,0:12:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝國的人 真會來進攻布魯魯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.26,0:12:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.82,0:12:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和詹姆也是自衛團的一員
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.87,0:12:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想被蒙在鼓裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.39,0:12:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝國…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.25,0:12:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「東歐帝國聯合」與「大西洋聯邦機構」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.25,0:12:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為爭奪Ragnite資源發動戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.92,0:12:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加利亞盛產Ragnite
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.37,0:12:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝國垂涎已久 恨不能將其據為己有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.05,0:13:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些上課時學過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.22,0:13:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.78,0:13:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加利亞為捍衛國土 必須抗擊侵略者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.38,0:13:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自衛團的職責是保護市民
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.61,0:13:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,具體部署正在討論
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.09,0:13:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能需要今天內疏散城市居民
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.61,0:13:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一到第三班負責疏解交通與戒備
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.19,0:13:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四班負責城內巡邏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.17,0:13:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我試著再去請求加利亞軍盡早出動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.96,0:13:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕來一個小隊 情況也會大為改觀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.79,0:13:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下只能祈禱帝國軍悠著點了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.46,0:14:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 艾麗西婭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.29,0:14:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不會吃槍子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.24,0:14:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被打之前開槍就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.69,0:14:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.20,0:14:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這種事我做不到的！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.12,0:14:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗西婭一點都不害怕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.48,0:14:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟是為了保衛布魯魯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.31,0:14:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他…他溜了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.32,0:14:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.87,0:14:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.68,0:14:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.54,0:14:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不站住就開槍了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.50,0:14:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的開槍了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.26,0:15:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃也沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.27,0:15:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.03,0:15:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝國軍！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.82,0:15:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偵察兵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.80,0:15:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經攻到這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.52,0:15:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.43,0:15:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你的人到底是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.46,0:15:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.94,0:15:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.20,0:16:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰的…你的妹妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.35,0:16:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.48,0:16:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才還在悠閒地寫生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.28,0:16:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹妹在等你的話 應該趕緊去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.25,0:16:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經常被人說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.76,0:16:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「做事的優先順序很奇怪」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.85,0:16:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 和你說話總是感覺莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.08,0:16:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.53,0:16:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.25,0:16:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是條件喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.04,0:16:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果圖謀不軌…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.42,0:16:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.53,0:16:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.69,0:16:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你家在哪兒？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.45,0:16:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.80,0:16:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這裡過去15分鐘的路程
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.32,0:16:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 這個方向是鞏特爾將軍的宅邸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.97,0:16:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臥倒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.79,0:16:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾出來 加利亞兵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.63,0:16:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑起來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.50,0:17:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.26,0:17:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面有門通向大屋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.53,0:17:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼對這幢房子瞭如指掌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.16,0:17:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是鞏特爾將軍的家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.40,0:17:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是第一次大戰中拯救加利亞的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.47,0:17:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.01,0:17:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.84,0:17:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經常被人說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.31,0:17:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是…鞏特爾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.75,0:17:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臥倒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.26,0:17:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可惡了 還緊追不捨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.78,0:17:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.91,0:18:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.65,0:18:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊莎拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.81,0:18:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.75,0:18:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.91,0:18:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.81,0:18:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來介紹 這位是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.26,0:18:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然在撒謊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.30,0:18:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撒謊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.32,0:18:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼自己是將軍的兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.22,0:18:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去接妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.48,0:18:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼妹妹 她是達魯庫斯人！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.94,0:18:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有騙你 伊莎拉是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.95,0:18:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舉起雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.09,0:19:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊莎拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.41,0:19:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倉庫裡有武器
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.86,0:19:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,型號雖然老舊 使用起來應該不成問題
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.57,0:19:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.00,0:19:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手榴彈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.44,0:19:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次大戰的遺產
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.60,0:19:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還能用呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.87,0:19:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有渾然天成的哥哥 才會有沉穩可靠的妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.69,0:20:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.24,0:20:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.68,0:20:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫艾麗西婭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.87,0:20:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗西婭·梅爾姬沃特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.65,0:20:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊莎拉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.49,0:20:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發誓今後未經允許 不對閃光鱒進行寫生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.83,0:20:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開火
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.76,0:20:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小看自衛團會如何…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.82,0:20:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘗嘗吧 帝國軍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.08,0:20:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.01,0:20:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀…失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.37,0:20:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠻游刃有餘啊 維爾金
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.80,0:20:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平安回去的話 請你吃三明治
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.45,0:21:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用上布魯魯最香的麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.48,0:21:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.64,0:21:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等…還有樣東西希望能派上用場
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.48,0:21:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許稍微大了些
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.65,0:21:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊莎拉 難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.13,0:21:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.81,0:21:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是它
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.68,0:21:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=======ED=======
